Well my parents left this mornin at like 12:30 for portland and then a concert in Vancover and so they wont be home till sunday at like 2:30ish. so im stayin here and bein bored i wishi had some one here to keep me company... im gettin bored. My parents think im stayin at travis' house tonite but really im stayin here... they dont trust me very much alone. i dunno why but they dont. well i think im gunna call it a nite... i mite be goin to a movie wit drina tomarrow and so im gunna need some sleep to make it thru the day, alright everyone im outtie!

My day was boring.

I WAS SOOOOO HOT TODAY i hate the sun! i wish that Kala could have joined us today damnit kala! 

I had a great time with you tho Audrina!

i want some ice cream... i think that im gunna go get some... so you will all hafta wait till tomarrow to find out how the ice cream was anyway adios!
